THis <normalised orig="Psalme" auto="true">Psalm</normalised> is a <normalised orig="Psalme" auto="true">Psalm</normalised> of thanksgiving,<lb/>
which David song <normalised orig="vnto" auto="true">unto</normalised> God,<lb/>
when <normalised orig="hee" auto="true">he</normalised> was first invested into his<lb/>
<normalised orig="kingdome" auto="true">kingdom</normalised>, and translated the <normalised orig="Arke" auto="true">Arc</normalised><lb/>
